WEBVTT

00:02.702 --> 00:05.869
You look so angry. What's wrong?

00:07.123 --> 00:09.708
I was making a plane out of paper.

00:10.112 --> 00:13.229
Then Paul came to me and hit me on the head.

00:15.475 --> 00:16.983
What are you doing, Dad?

00:18.013 --> 00:19.538
I'm making a table.

00:20.683 --> 00:23.709
Wow. Are you making a table out of wood?

00:24.783 --> 00:28.417
That's right. These chairs are also made of wood.

00:29.684 --> 00:32.643
My baby brother always teases me.

00:33.791 --> 00:36.815
Does he? What does he usually do?

00:38.009 --> 00:41.565
He pulls me by the hair and hits me on the arm.

